===Definitions===
{{head|zh|hanzi}}

# to [[stick]] [[into]]; to [[insert]]; to [[poke]]; to [[pierce]]
#: {{zh-x|把 紅 旗 插 上 頂峰|to stick the red flag into the summit}}
#: {{zh-x|插 支 香|to stand up a joss stick|C}}
# to [[interpose]]; to [[insert]]; to [[cut in]]
#: {{zh-x|她 突然 插 了 一句。|She suddenly cut in to speak.}}
# to [[participate]]; to [[take part]] in; to [[mix]]; to [[mingle]]
# {{lb|zh|literary}} to [[plant]]
# {{lb|zh|Cantonese}} to [[scold]]; to [[criticize]]
# {{lb|zh|Eastern Min|Hokkien|Singapore Teochew}} to [[take notice]] of; to [[pay attention]] to; to [[heed]]
# {{lb|zh|Southern Min}} to [[support]] someone by the [[armpit]]
# {{lb|zh|Hokkien}} to [[interfere]]; to [[intervene]]; to [[meddle]]
# {{lb|zh|Mainland China|_|Hokkien}} to [[pin]] something to one's [[waist]], etc.
# {{lb|zh|Mainland China|_|Hokkien}} to [[mix]] up; to [[jumble]] up
# {{lb|zh|Mainland China|_|Hokkien|card games}} to [[shuffle]]
# {{lb|zh|Taiwanese Hokkien}} to [[bet]]; to [[wager]]
# {{lb|zh|Zhangzhou Hokkien}} to [[kidnap]] {{gl|for ransom}}
# {{alt form|zh|鍤|t=[[spade]]; [[shovel]]}}

